=== TASK ===
# Client Portal (No-Login Link)

## Overview
Build a mobile-first, no-login client portal experience that is accessed via a secure, tokenized link. Clients can view and compare Decision Cards, comment with mentions and attachments, and approve decisions. The portal should be branded per studio, support optional custom domains, provide in-app and email notifications, maintain an audit trail, and export decision logs. All interactions are token-authenticated, read/write where appropriate, and do not require a user account for access.

## Page Description (Full Detail)
What this page is:
- The Client Portal (No-Login Link) page is a client-facing, token-authenticated interface optimized for mobile devices. It presents one or more Decision Cards (Decision Objects) with side-by-side option comparison, threaded comments, and clear approve/reject/confirm actions. It includes a project header with branding, a simplified navigation system suitable for mobile, and a secure token expiry/security notice.

Goals:
- Provide a frictionless, high-clarity path for clients to review decisions, discuss, and approve via a tokenized link without creating an account.
- Ensure auditability with timestamps, authoring users (studio side), and a robust activity history.
- Enable branding options (logo, color scheme, optional custom domain) for client-facing links.
- Trigger transactional emails and in-app notifications for approvals, comments, and exports, with mentions support.
- Support attachments (documents, drawings, specs) and file sharing in comments.
- Facilitate subsequent actions: sharing the decision, exporting decision logs, and creating follow-up tasks.

Connected features:
- Responsive Navigation: Mobile-first navigation with a collapsible sidebar and topbar for global actions (e.g., help, support, branding switcher).
- Notifications (Email & In-App): Triggered for approvals, reminders, comments, and exports; includes mention notifications.
- Decision Objects & Approval Workflow (Core): Core data model for decisions, options, comments, approvals, audit trail, and export-ready logs.
- Branding & Custom Client Links: Studio-level branding including logo, color palette, and optional custom domain at the client link level.
- Comments, Mentions & Collaboration: Threaded comments with user mentions, inline attachments, and email/in-app notifications when mentioned or replied to.
- Client Portal (No-login) Experience: Tokenized access path with secure, time-bound links; low-friction review/approval UI.
- Asset Kit: Icon Set & Illustrations for UI components and marketing.
- Success / Confirmation Page: Generic confirmation after actions like approval or export readiness.
- Decision Detail Page: Comprehensive view of a Decision Card with visual comparison, comments, approval status, history, attachments, and actions (share, export, create follow-up task).

Visual guidance:
- Consistent with the project’s branding and design system (see Visual Style).
- Emphasize readability, quick scanning, and clear affordances for actions.

